article.description: — Ryan Zan's 19 points helped La Salle defeat Rosemont 107-41 on Thursday.
article.headline: La Salle takes down Rosemont 107-41
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- — Ryan Zan's 19 points helped La Salle defeat Rosemont 107-41 on Thursday. Zan added seven rebounds and three steals for the Explorers (9-3). Rokas Jocius scored 15 points and added six rebounds and three blocks. Daeshon Shepherd shot 5 of 5 from the field to finish with 12 points. The Ravens were led by Dejuan Taylor, who posted eight points. Zaki Gomez added eight points for Rosemont. In addition, Denelle Holly finished with seven points. ---- The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
